Name: Don't Die! Douche!
About the game: Charge your way through 5 fever-dream precision platformer worlds, dodging a plethora of bizarre dangers on your way. And remember: Don't Die! Douche! ...Except That You Will Die... A Lot! This uncompromising love letter to the rage games of old has been purposely crafted to annoy, upset and enrage you! Over 20 perilous levels, spread across 5 worlds full of weirdness and legally ambiguous parody Discover shocking secrets that will make you question your own sanity (or at least that of the creator!) Your chance to achieve a range of speed ratings for each level - Can you Gold them all? Not at all annoying soundtrack
